g.title: Semigroup
g.text: ∀a b c. (a + b) + c = a + (b + c)

g.title: LeftSeminearring
g.text: a * (b + c) = a * b + a * c

g.title: RightSeminearring
g.text: (a + b) * c = a * c + b * c

g.title: Eq
g.text: ∀a b c. a == b and b == c → a == c

g.title: POrd
g.text: a == b = a ≥ b and b ≥ a
∀a b c. a ≥ b and b ≥ c → a ≥ c

g.title: MeetSemilattice
g.text: ∀a b c. a ∧ (b ∧ c) = (a ∧ b) ∧ c

g.title: JoinSemilattice
g.text: ∀a b c. a ∨ (b ∨ c) = (a ∨ b) ∨ c

g.title: Ord
g.text: ∀a b. a ≥ b or b ≥ a
a ∧ b | a ≥ b → b | b ≥ a → a
a ∨ b | a ≥ b → a | b ≥ a → b
